description:
Labybox puts you to the test with intricate maze filled with traps! Make your way with your ball moving boxes and do not get stuck in dead ends. Moving boxes as you like along the route through which you can create you new ways to reach the goal or get stuck with your own hands! Use the boxes to overcome the pitfalls that hides the maze. Engaged to solve the maze in the shortest possible time and challenge yourself to improve your time!

Now with 5 more levels!!

►Features

☻Intuitive controls with accelerometer and touch
☻25 different levels
☻High-end 3D graphics
☻High degree of challenge

Levels and updates soon available!!
